name: MAYBELLINE NEW YORK COLOSSAL VOLUME EXPRESS WATERPROOF MASCARA BLACK
description: A bold, collagen-infused formula with an iconic applicator brush that would give each and every lash a bold touch. Only one swipe of this colossal mascara by Maybelline is enough to give your lashes the volume and thickness you desire. Use an eyelash curler before application for the best results.
